title: Major bushfires threaten Perth homes | 7NEWS
description: Major bushfires are burning across Perth, with emergency blazes threatening homes in Kenwick and Bullsbrook. The Kenwick fire has scorched almost 100 hectares, forcing evacuations and temporarily closing Perth Airport's main runway. Strong gusty winds up to 43 kilometres per hour and temperatures above 36 degrees have created extreme bushfire conditions, with over 100 firefighters battling the out-of-control blazes.
